---
title: Seared Steak with Crispy Potato Salad
description: Our Spanish-inspired potato salad boasts crispy potatoes, briny olives, and fresh green beans for a salad like you’ve never tasted before. It’s hard to compete with a juicy pan-seared steak, but this
salad definitely gives that steak a run for its money.
